          <li>Scale cleaning padded into flat rate</li>
          <li>You may pay for parts you don&rsquo;t need</li>
          <li>Hard water root cause may go unfixed</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="tr-card us">
        <h3>Our approach &mdash; labor + parts separate</h3>
        <ul class="tr-list">
          <li>Diagnose first, including hard water assessment</li>
          <li>Labor and parts as separate line items</li>
          <li>Scale-only repairs cost less &mdash; no parts needed</li>
          <li>Root cause fixed, not just the symptom</li>
          <li>$89 diagnostic applied to the total</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

