    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How much does dishwasher repair cost in Los Angeles?</div><div class="faq-a">Labor typically runs $150&ndash;$320 for standard brands. Parts are quoted separately after diagnosis. The $89 diagnostic fee applies to the repair total when you approve the work. Miele luxury dishwashers run $250&ndash;$520+ in labor due to European OEM parts.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Why do you quote labor and parts separately?</div><div class="faq-a">Many LA repair companies use flat-rate BlueBook pricing. A spray arm clogged by LA hard water &mdash; no parts needed &mdash; should not cost the same as a drain pump replacement. We quote separately so the price reflects your actual repair.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Does LA hard water really affect dishwasher repair costs?</div><div class="faq-a">Significantly. Los Angeles water runs 300&ndash;400 mg/L TDS &mdash; well above the national average. Spray arms clog, heating elements scale up, and detergent dispensers jam. Many dishwasher calls in LA are scale-related and require no replacement part. We always check for hard water root causes before quoting a parts repair.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Are parts included in the quoted labor price?</div><div class="faq-a">No &mdash; all prices on this page are labor only. After diagnosis we quote the specific part needed as a separate line item. Descaling and cleaning are included in the repair when hard water is the root cause &mdash; not a separate charge. OEM parts used wherever available.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How much does Miele dishwasher repair cost in Los Angeles?</div><div class="faq-a">Labor for Miele dishwasher repair runs $250&ndash;$520+ depending on the failure. Miele uses proprietary European components at a premium price. Parts are quoted separately so you see exactly what the OEM Miele components cost.</div></div>
